# Otterdays Site Agent

**Read `AGENTS.md` at repo root** before non-trivial work. Static GitHub Pages site — HTML/CSS/vanilla JS, no build step.

## Must-know placement

| Page | Content |
|------|---------|
| `chats.html` | First-party **lab** chats by **country** only |
| `other-assistants.html` | Hubs & specialty (Perplexity, OpenRouter, Poe, T3 Chat, Duck.ai) |
| `tools.html` | Dev tools; agents in `#computer-automation` (curated order, not A–Z) |
| `companies.html` | Every organization on the site |
| `specials.html` | Moltbook, free domains, learning, games |

**Hub ≠ lab.** Multi-model routers go on Other Assistants, not Provider Chats.

## Every new link item

1. HTML card on correct page
2. `js/search-data.js` entry
3. `js/badges.js` if country flag needed (key = exact `.chat-link-name`)
4. `companies.html` if new org
5. `DOCS/SCRATCHPAD.md` + `DOCS/CHANGELOG.md`

Full checklist: `DOCS/CONTENT_GUIDE.md`.

## Releases

Bump `js/updates-data.js`, all HTML `vX.Y.Z` badges, `DOCS/CHANGELOG.md` — only when user ships a version. Do not commit/push unless asked.

## Constraints

- Windows shell: `;` not `&&`
- Sidebar nav must stay identical across all `*.html` (🌐 for Other Assistants — never `??`)
- Minimize scope; read files before editing
- Current version: **v1.11.0**
